                <p>Odds and lines subject to change. 21+ (18+ NH/WY). Physically present in AZ / CO / CT / IL / IN / IA / KS / LA (select parishes) / MA / MD / MI / NH / NJ / NY / OH / OR / PA / TN / VA / WV / WY only. Void in ONT. Eligibility restrictions apply. See terms at draftkings.com/sportsbook. On behalf of Boot Hill Casino & resort (KS).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg12 col-md-12">
                    <section class="copyright"><a href="{{@site.url}}">{{@site.title}}</a> &copy; {{date format="YYYY"}} All Rights Reserved.</section>
                </div>
            </div>

          </div>    
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </footer><!-- End Footer -->
  <div id="preloader"></div>

</main>
{{!-- /.viewport --}}


{{!-- Scripts - handle member signups, responsive videos, infinite scroll, floating headers, and galleries --}}
